    <dcterms:title>Playing Santa Claus, and Other Christmas Tales</dcterms:title>
    <dcterms:tableOfContents>Playing Santa Claus -- Nothing to give -- Willie's gold dollar -- The Thanksgiving party -- A Christmas story -- April Fool's day -- The Christmas tree -- A dream -- No time like the present -- The little match boy -- I forgot -- The silver morning and golden day -- Two sides to a story.</dcterms:tableOfContents>
